			· now detaches itself from CLI
			· added option to process last file again
			· display after search was messed in certain
			  cases

	My harddisk crashed so I was interrupted 1 month. Life's
	a bitch sometimes ...

V1.02ß	(12.09.93)	· added option to select other filetype
			· fixed "bug" in File-Recognition-routine that
			  recognised DMS-files as ASCII-files, if they
			  had Ansi-logos added to them
			· "Deselect Files"-confirmation requester now
