			· Added ResultWindow while DePack!ing, to make
			  process more transparent to the user
			· Quit/PrefsEdit didn't worked when hotkey
			  (Amiga-Q/E) was used. Fixed.
			· Partial deselection of processed files now
			  possible
			· Improved Manual

	Changed Version system to an autobumping system. So the next
	version/revision # after V1.02ß is 38.0

38.29	(02.10.1993)	· Version system changed to more intelligent thing.
			  Thanx to John Preston for the program.
			· Results are displayed after DePack!ing
			· More intelligent window system
			· Added some menus and help stuff
			· PatternMatching function added. All lines
			  that contain an entered string will be high-
			  lighted in color #3 
			· Dirreading much faster (3x)

	Two weeks peace ... a little break from coding

38.66	(28.10.1993)	· Added three new features : Jump to line/entry
			  and insert entry
			· Last line of dirfile wasn't read 100%. Fixed.
			· Added online Amigaguide-Hypertext (yell from
